trast, for almost all the others\nSGRs/AXPs, $\\log L_X$ does not vary too much as function of $\\log \\dot{E}_{\\rm\nrot}$, a phenomenology not shared by X-ray neutron star pulsars, suggesting a\ndifferent nature for these sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jul 2013 22:10:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-01"}
