lated triads} in this case. Resonant\ntriads are interconnected in a complicated way and the smallest cluster\nconsists of 6 connected triads.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Jul 2013 10:24:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-01"}
