mponents are closer to each\nother and winner/loser components are separable on elastic maps for HANGSENG\nand DAX index while for the negative possibility indices, there is no sign of\nseparation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Jul 2013 12:56:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
